concrete examples

example 1: rerun with one change

user:

run last wan22 gen with red armor

llm:
	•	finds last wan22 artifact
	•	copies source generator
	•	changes one field

cdi:

$$$$rerun-last-wan22

$$$source
$artifact
v0009123

$$$override

$armor
red

cli:

beast run /tmp/rerun-last-wan22.cdi


